ledge of the optical properties of the galaxies. Further\nefforts are required to demonstrate that this model can be used to produce\nlarge ensembles of mock galaxy catalogues for upcoming surveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Aug 2022 11:41:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Aug 2022 07:24:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 1 Sep 2022 09:01:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-12"}
