RLVSC\ncan achieve over 39% BD-rate saving for video semantic coding under the Low\nDelay P configuration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Aug 2022 13:22:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-25"}
