y reduce congestion, and their effects can differ both\ntemporally and spatially. However, they can have potential side effects such as\nincreased purchase and usage of new energy vehicles, owners of which can obtain\na local license plate of Shanghai for free.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Aug 2022 14:32:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 15 Jan 2023 10:06:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-18"}
